  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      It's a monitoring study. The aim is to assess the progression free survival up to 3 years.
      Patients are not treated until progression. Search for scalability predictive factors and
      registration of treatments if progression.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
